## CE QUI DOIT ÊTRE AJOUTÉ / RESTAURÉ

### Variables globales à ajouter
```javascript
let _focusedOrgan = null;
let _focusedContent = null;
let _mdX = 0, _mdY = 0;
```

### CSS à ajouter (dans <style>)
```css
#focus-overlay {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: rgba(240,239,235,0.75);
  z-index: 100;
  cursor: default;
}
.organ-container.focused {
  z-index: 200;
  min-width: 420px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}
```

### Fonction enterFocus(card) à ajouter
```javascript
function enterFocus(card) {
  if (_focusedOrgan) return;
  _focusedContent = card.innerHTML;
  _focusedOrgan = card;

  const overlay = document.createElement('div');
  overlay.id = 'focus-overlay';
  document.getElementById('genome-canvas').appendChild(overlay);

  document.querySelectorAll('.organ-container').forEach(c => {
    if (c !== card) { c.style.opacity = '0.28'; c.style.pointerEvents = 'none'; }
  });
  card.classList.add('focused');

  // Trouver l'organe dans le genome
  const organId = card.dataset.organId;
  let organ = null;
  for (const phase of (_genome?.n0_phases || [])) {
    organ = (phase.n1_sections || []).find(o => o.id === organId);
    if (organ) break;
  }
  if (!organ) return;

  // Contenu détaillé
  card.innerHTML = '';
  const header = document.createElement('div');
  header.style.cssText = 'display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 10px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0efeb;margin-bottom:6px;';
  header.innerHTML = `<span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#3d3d3c;">${organ.name}</span><button id="focus-close" style="background:none;border:none;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;color:#999;line-height:1;">✕</button>`;
  card.appendChild(header);

  const body = document.createElement('div');
  body.style.cssText = 'max-height:500px;overflow-y:auto;padding:6px 10px;';
  for (const feat of (organ.n2_features || [])) {
    const ft = document.createElement('p');
    ft.style.cssText = 'font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#999;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:10px 0 5px;';
    ft.textContent = feat.name;
    body.appendChild(ft);
    for (const comp of (feat.n3_components || [])) {
      const cw = document.createElement('div');
      cw.style.marginBottom = '6px';
      cw.innerHTML = _comp_html(comp);
      const cn = document.createElement('p');
      cn.style.cssText = 'font-size:9px;color:#aaa;margin:2px 0 0 2px;';
      cn.textContent = comp.name;
      cw.appendChild(cn);
      body.appendChild(cw);
    }
  }
  card.appendChild(body);

  // Listeners exit
  overlay.addEventListener('click', exitFocus, { once: true });
  document.getElementById('focus-close').addEventListener('click', exitFocus, { once: true });
}
```

### Fonction exitFocus() à ajouter
```javascript
function exitFocus() {
  const overlay = document.getElementById('focus-overlay');
  if (overlay) overlay.remove();
  document.querySelectorAll('.organ-container').forEach(c => {
    c.style.opacity = '';
    c.style.pointerEvents = '';
  });
  if (_focusedOrgan) {
    _focusedOrgan.classList.remove('focused');
    _focusedOrgan.innerHTML = _focusedContent;
    // Réappend resize handles
    const rh = document.createElement('div');
    rh.className = 'resize-handle';
    _focusedOrgan.appendChild(rh);
    const rhs = document.createElement('div');
    rhs.className = 'resize-handle-s';
    _focusedOrgan.appendChild(rhs);
    _focusedOrgan = null;
    _focusedContent = null;
  }
}
```

### Dans initDragAndDrop() — tracking mousedown coords + trigger focus
Dans le mousedown listener principal (le canvas.addEventListener qui gère drag/resize), ajouter en TOUT DÉBUT du listener :
```javascript
_mdX = e.clientX;
_mdY = e.clientY;
```

Dans le mouseup listener (document.addEventListener('mouseup')), après les blocs resizedHeightOrgan et resizedOrgan, AVANT le bloc draggedOrgan — ajouter la détection focus :
```javascript
// Click = pas de mouvement + c'était une carte (pas resize)
if (!resizedHeightOrgan && !resizedOrgan && draggedOrgan) {
  const dist = Math.hypot(e.clientX - _mdX, e.clientY - _mdY);
  if (dist < 5) {
    const cardToFocus = draggedOrgan;
    draggedOrgan = null;
    document.body.style.userSelect = '';
    enterFocus(cardToFocus);
    return;
  }
}
```

### Keyboard listener (Escape uniquement)
```javascript
document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
  if (e.key === 'Escape' && _focusedOrgan) exitFocus();
});
```

